results.name: a(n) = Sum_{1 <= x_1 <= x_2 <= x_3 <= x_4 <= n} gcd(x_1, x_2, x_3 , x_4, n).
mathematica: a[n_] := DivisorSum[n, EulerPhi[n/#] * Binomial[# + 3, 4] &]; Array[a, 50] (* _Amiram Eldar_, Apr 18 2021 *)
program: (PARI) a(n) = sum(a=1, n, sum(b=1, a, sum(c=1, b, sum(d=1, c, gcd(gcd(gcd(gcd(n, a), b), c), d)))));
results.author: _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 17 2021
